    <string name="help_singleplayer">Singleplayer</string>
    <string name="help_multiplayer">Multiplayer</string>
    <string name="help_singleplayer_content">
        When you enter the Singleplayer mode, you see two dices. After the dice cup covers them up,
        you can shake the cup, by shaking your phone. As soon as you stop shaking, the cup uncovers
        the dices again. \n\nIf you throw doubles, you have the possibility to shake the cup again.
        All scores are added together at the end of the game.
    </string>
    <string name="help_multiplayer_content">To play the Multiplayer, your opponent needs to be right
        next to you. The game is using Bluetooth and/or WiFi to connect to your opponent. For this,
        you will be asked for permission. After accepting, press the button <i>Find Opponent</i>. When
        you found your opponent, the game directly starts. \n\nLike in the Singleplayer mode, you
        need to shake your phone to get a score. After both of you played, the results are shown.
        You can now continue your game by pressing <i>Continue</i>. If you or your opponent presses the
        back button or turns off the display, you are disconnected and you are not able to continue
        the game.
    </string>

